flowchart TD
  PLAN[Plan change]
  CODE[Edit declarative config]
  TEST[Test locally and in namespace]
  APPLY[Install/Rebuild apply]
  BOOT[Bootstrap reconcile]
  VERIFY[verify-flow and smoke tests]
  PROMOTE[Promote to primary namespace]
  MONITOR[Observe + backup drills]

  PLAN --> CODE --> TEST --> APPLY --> BOOT --> VERIFY --> PROMOTE --> MONITOR --> PLAN
